title: Green Witch's Cauldron Sound Pack
description: Prepare the Herbs, Roots and Who Knows What for Your Magic Cauldron! Your Fresh Recipes Out Now from Top Witches of Vadi Sound!
longDescription: Green Witch’s Cauldron Sound Effects Bundle brings you the sounds of healing white magic. It includes collecting and drying herbs, bubbling boiling potions, bottling, casting spells with elemental magic, and many more you can find in a cauldron. With this bundle, you will have access to cat sounds, witch reactions, dried seeds, dried herbs, defensive spells, transfiguration spells. Green Witch’s Cauldron Sound Effects Bundle was recorded and designed exquisitely for all your magical needs and covers all sound effects needs for any white magic, potion-brewing, project and games that you are working on.
